@node about "About FullTime"
About Full Time
---------------    
   Full Time is a football results prediction program for the Amiga. It
predicts both wins and draws and can be used to help pick teams for fixed
odds betting, or as a pools prediction program.

    It predicts the outcome of each match, and rates the most likely
results, using a '*' system. Likely draws are shown with a 'D'

    FullTime's functionality is limited until the program has been registered. It will only predict the results of the first two divisions (English Premiership and Division 1), and outputing the results to a printer is disabled.

   It will allow you to enter the fixtures of every division, and update
the results, allowing you to keep all the data up to date, if you are thinking of registering it.
@endnode

